        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Unexpected Findings After 41 Hours Testing</h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider font-black">What nobody tells estate planners about websites</p>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-amber-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Process explained: 5x more qualified consultations</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Attorney had vague process. Added "Step 1: Consult, Step 2: Draft, Step 3: Sign" prominently. Month 1: 5x more booked consultations. Clear process = comfort = hire you.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-amber-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Services clear: 4x better client fit</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Added "Living Trusts, Wills, Power of Attorney" prominently. Month 1: 4x more qualified calls. Clear services = you solve my need = hire you.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-amber-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
