            <span class="text-amber-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Mobile booking: 73% of families search on phones</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Family discussion = search on phone. Non-responsive site = skip this attorney. Mobile-optimized booking = they engage. Planning = mobile search.</p>
            </div>
