          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-2">Explore AI builders for law firms and attorneys</p>
          <a href="/best-ai-website-builder-for-law-firms" class="text-amber-600 font-semibold hover:underline text-sm">View Law Firms Guide â†’</a>
